These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
There 4 different types of food: peas, lettuce, spinach, grapefruit
There are 4 different nationalities: malaysian, canadian, spanish, nigerian
1. the canadian is on the left of the malaysian##1
2. the person eating peas is the nigerian##1
3. the spanish is on the right of the malaysian##1
4. the person eating lettuce is on the left of the nigerian##1
5. the person eating grapefruit is on the left of the malaysian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | grapefruit | spinach | lettuce | peas   |
| Nationality   | canadian  | malaysian     | spanish   | nigerian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, puzzles, skydiving, singing
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, surfing, skiing, ice-hockey
1. the person who's hobby is singing is the person who's sport is surfing##1
2. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the far right##1
3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
4. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
5. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby   | skydiving | singing | puzzles | collecting    |
| Sport   | skiing    | surfing      | lacrosse | ice-hockey |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, filmmaking, drawing, dancing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, satire, scientific, thriller
1. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is the person watching comedy movies##1
3. the person watching satire movies is on the far right##1
4. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
5. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| Hobby         | hiking | dancing | drawing   | filmmaking |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy   | scientific | thriller | satire         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: mystery, horror, satire, thriller
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, lacrosse, ice-hockey, baseball
1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the person watching thriller movies##1
2. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
3. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
4. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
5. the person who's sport is soccer is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | horror | mystery  | satire      |
| Sport         | lacrosse | baseball   | ice-hockey | soccer |

