.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-5::.
There 4 different types of food: apricot, grapefruit, artichoke, corn
4 different pets are kept: goat, goldfish, cat, horse
1. the person eating grapefruit is on the left of the person eating apricot##1
2. the owner of the cat is on the right of the person eating artichoke##1
3. the person eating corn is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
4. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the owner of the cat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |  2   |    3     |      4      |
| Food   | corn | artichoke | grapefruit | apricot |
| Pet    | goat       | horse | cat | goldfish     |

