.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-6::.
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, japanese, brazilian, italian
4 different pets are kept: snake, cat, rat, pony
1. the japanese is on the far right##1
2. the italian is on the left of the brazilian##1
3. the owner of the pony is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
4. the owner of the snake is on the left of the brazilian##1
5. the owner of the pony is on the right of the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| Nationality   | italian | brazilian | australian | japanese |
| Pet           | snake      | rat | pony | cat    |

