.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-7::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, pop, dubstep, soul
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, snake, pony, dog
1. the owner of the pony is on the far left##1
2. the fan of soul is on the far right##1
3. the fan of dubstep is on the far left##1
4. the owner of the snake is on the far right##1
5. the fan of pop is on the left of the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |     3     |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep | pop | hip-hop | soul  |
| Pet           | pony | guinea-pig | dog       | snake |

