.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-8::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  librarian, freelancer, teacher, manager
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, airplane, bike, bus
1. the person driving the bus is on the right of the freelancer##1
2. the person driving the bus is the manager##1
3. the freelancer is on the right of the librarian##1
4. the teacher is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
5. the person driving the jet-ski is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |    3     |    4     |
| Job         | teacher | librarian      | freelancer | manager |
| Transport   | jet-ski          | airplane | bike     | bus    |

