3. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the far right##1
4. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
5. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |   3    |    4     |
