.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, fanta, coffee, tea
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, jet-ski, skateboard, scooter
1. the person driving the van is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
2. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
3. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
4. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |       3       |   4    |
| Beverage    | 7up | coffee  | fanta | tea |
| Transport   | scooter | skateboard | jet-ski          | van    |

