.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, almond-milk, 7up, coffee
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, house, indie, techno
1. the fan of indie is on the right of the fan of funk##1
2. the fan of techno is on the right of the fan of indie##1
3. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
4. the person drinking 7up is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking almond-milk is the fan of indie##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |       3       |   4   |
| Beverage      | 7up | almond-milk  | iced-tea | coffee |
| Music-Genre   | funk  | indie | techno           | house   |

