5. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |   2    |   3    |    4    |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | fanta  | almond-milk | milk   |
| Pet        | frog | turtle | cat    | chinchilla |

