3. the person watching western movies is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
4. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
5. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |      3      |    4    |
