.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-20::.
There are 4 different nationalities: french, italian, malaysian, thai
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, train, motorbike, taxi
1. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the italian##1
2. the person driving the train is on the left of the thai##1
3. the french is on the left of the malaysian##1
4. the thai is the person driving the taxi##1
5. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the italian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Nationality   | french | malaysian | italian | thai   |
| Transport     | motorbike  | jet-ski    | train       | taxi |

 